{"tid":1806834,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"德國男粉跟蹤TWICE搭同班機！ 「全程瘋狂接近娜璉」機內陷入混亂","createTime":"2020-01-01T13:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T03:32:48.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"eb3fd3c9b457ee4ffe501db77afce16faeb7c1f5","tid":1806834,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T13:53:42.000Z","msg":"TWICE德國男粉絲被朋友揭露「幻想娜璉是自己女朋友」，且實際飛到南韓首爾並四處打聽對方行蹤消息曝光後，讓全世界ONCE（官方粉絲名稱）都相當擔心。沒想到1日TWICE搭乘飛機回韓時，該名男粉絲竟然也搭乘同台飛機並試圖接近，場面一片混亂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4617/4617920.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4617%2F4617920.jpg&h=2a5430b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲德國跟蹤狂粉絲曾預告12月會再去南韓，沒想到竟然和TWICE搭同班飛機。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\nJYP娛樂1日中午於TWICE官方頁面發出公告：「今天在從日本回國的飛機上，成員娜璉的海外跟蹤狂搭乘同台飛機並不停試圖接近成員本人，在機內引起了混亂，雖然因為即時應對沒讓成員受到直接性的傷害，但她不斷透露不便和不安的心情。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4617/d4617833.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4617%2Fd4617833.jpg&h=ebb3d20c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲娜璉飽受狂粉困擾。（圖／翻攝自TWICE IG）<br />\n<br />\n從1日回國影片中可見，娜璉戴著毛帽不停和Sana講話，看起來疲憊又不安的模樣讓人相當心疼，面對大批媒體和粉絲不像過去大方打招呼或收下信件和禮物，而是低頭快速走過，心情似乎受到相當大的影響。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4617/d4617832.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4617%2Fd4617832.jpg&h=2719d292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE於1日回國影片。（圖／翻攝自비몽YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n對此，JYP娛樂透露已經多次向德國跟蹤狂表示「請不要試圖接近成員」並且嚴厲警告，甚至就連警方也親自出面警示對方，但該男子完全沒有反省或停止不當行為。因此，公司已經採取最高強度的法律措施並加強保全，另外也對販售藝人航班訊息的非法狀況進行瞭解：「我司以本次案件作為契機將嘗試各種可以根除犯罪的方案。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gU7vcWfl4EE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgU7vcWfl4EE&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIc%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=fd308822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gU7vcWfl4EE</a>"},{"pid":"3c25d777ef2c86abe3ef8548d5f9c684b5d9ab84","tid":1806834,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814354012a33d17c6052ba50d205cf986bff750b","tid":1806834,"uid":46435,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T13:56:52.000Z","msg":"其實大肉腸做錯左d咩..=="},{"pid":"711ae07afa1adb9bc125fdf1881bf341ec0461c7","tid":1806834,"uid":208486,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T13:58:16.000Z","msg":"娜璉好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedc373f26f19be0467b751d0e6c583ceffe82c8","tid":1806834,"uid":143093,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T13:58:37.000Z","msg":"跟蹤下都唔係好過份姐"},{"pid":"f7cd4069347feea514f1f49ab0ee4ec581e2a3be","tid":1806834,"uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eedc373f26f19be0467b751d0e6c583ceffe82c8","tid":1806834,"uid":143093,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T13:58:37.000Z","msg":"跟蹤下都唔係好過份姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T13:59:11.000Z","msg":"JYP又借D意做新聞"},{"pid":"7052096f5a4bdd3926d0d46eec78e8deae095eec","tid":1806834,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:00:22.000Z","msg":"戲子佬"},{"pid":"d070f436d497692a5390523c9754c8843eae87b4","tid":1806834,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:01:54.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗痴得咁暈循"},{"pid":"cb46bf043529e6a3d3dc84cf4741cc7d5069c228","tid":1806834,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:03:19.000Z","msg":"娜璉其實好想俾屌啦 一路插一路掃自己豆豆嗰隻"},{"pid":"6a0e794f2ff20f482f556601a836828da76bdd17","tid":1806834,"uid":110207,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:09:34.000Z","msg":"痴漢頂點<br />\n連偶像本人都知佢存在 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144a1dce41096162b00085ccc624b57c099a25